{"tid":1137580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣囝囝做白馬王子 Jayden馬上展chok樣","createTime":"2019-05-04T01:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T02:03:57.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c3009f395b62485a15242adf25880a11c70c2a19","tid":1137580,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"李嘉欣和老公許晉亨不時拍拖入馬場，撐擁有的愛駒，未知是否受到父母薰陶，他們8歲多的囝囝許建彤（Jayden Max）都喜歡騎馬，嘉欣也讓兒子去學騎馬，Jayden的馬術技巧都不錯。<br />\n<br />\n嘉欣趁着復活節假期，就帶了囝囝Jayden去旅遊，她今日在IG Story上載了這個Happy Trip的照片，當中看到Jayden騎馬的英姿，他騎着白馬在沙圈練習，戴了黑超的Jayden還展示chok樣，這位前世情人一笑，當然冧爆媽咪，Jayden還騎馬到街上踱步。相片還看到Jayden玩爬繩網和踩單車，身手敏捷，也有大美人媽咪嘉欣的淡妝自拍，此行也有Jayden同齡玩伴，但照片未見許晉亨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ne2AFfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fne2AFfO.png&h=df0d3e1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">李嘉欣陪囝囝去度假。（IG圖片）</span>"},{"pid":"ac394fa913e4453603a936bb7721f6bf92e966c2","tid":1137580,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNPSHuO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNPSHuO.png&h=fa29c8fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Jayden騎馬不忘來個chok樣。</span>"},{"pid":"b99b00a532a79c516ec35706830975298fdd8f38","tid":1137580,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"美人IG都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb3e41863802e63a645354be5bea56563f246fc","tid":1137580,"uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"你無諗住做白馬王子你chok樣來把撚呀？"}]}